OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunny spells turning hazy, as cloud
OL,7,Frapidly thickens from the west. Rain
OL,8,Fmoving east overnight, turning heavy
OL,9,Fand persistent in some southern
OL,10,Fregions, before probably easing and
OL,11,Fbecoming more showery later. Turning
OL,12,Fwindier with coastal gales in the
OL,13,Fsouthwest.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FA cloudy, cool and often wet
OL,16,Fday with periods of rain, heavy and
OL,17,Fpersistent at times. Brighter for some
OL,18,Flater. Windy at times with gales
OL,19,Fpossibly developing in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
