OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand windy on Sunday with occasional
OL,7,Fheavy rain in the north and west,
OL,8,Fspreading southeast later. Rain
OL,9,Fclearing to sunny spells on Monday.
OL,10,FSunshine and blustery showers on
OL,11,FTuesday.
